현진아 꿈에서 봤어 공항같은 곳에 다들 모여있었는데 방창한테 같이 사진 찍어도 되냐고 했는데 안됐어 나도 다 물어봐 , 그런데 아무도 허락하지 않았어요. 오직 당신만이 당신과 함께 사진을 찍는 것을 허락했습니다. 그리고 우리는 당신과 함께 우리 어머니 집으로 갑니다. 거기에는 우리 할머니들도 계시는데 당신을 매우 사랑한다고 하십니다. 그 후에는 당신을 데려갑니다. 저는 터키 사람이기 때문에 초등학교 4년, 중학교 4년, 고등학교 4년, 대학교 2년입니다. 저는 현재 중등학교 6년입니다. . 내 수업. 어쨌든 우리는 너와 함께 우리 학교에 가는데 거기서 너를 보는 사람들이 네 주위로 모인다. 그리고 8학년들이 너를 7/E반으로 데려다준다. 마지막으로 거기서 보자. 몇 분 후 네가 없는 것을 깨닫고 교장실로 갔으나 교장실을 찾을 수 없었다. 나는 막 잠에서 깨어났다. 내가 교장을 찾는 동안.

text: I am infuriated by non-voting stays. Don't they really understand that love alone is VERY MUCH NOT enough. No one gives desana for beautiful eyes, does not take ambassadors, and certainly does not allocate a huge budget for clips. Do they want to return to the District 9 era? For clips with two images and locations and with 0 graphics and special effects? So let's not do anything and we'll get back to where we started very quickly. But it's a pity for the guys that all their hard work and efforts, all the sleepless nights are going to hell. Because it's too difficult for someone to pick up a phone that I'm 100% sure won't let go of their hands and watch a freaking advertisement, at least an hour a day. In the same hour, you can safely collect 100 tickets, and if the advertising goes well, then all 200. We're collecting these damn tickets from DECEMBER 8th, until the end of voting - that's 41 days. This is 4100 without strain, and in the best case, all 8200. This is a huge help for the final vote. But no, we'll watch the edits, drool, write obscene comments, and on winning some nomination we'll write: "Well, my, well, handsome." No one asks us to sit in this khuzfan for days, one fucking hour a day, not to watch tt, but to watch ads. it's not difficult. Just laziness. "And why? There are a lot of them, they can handle it without me." And on the next loss: "Damn, it's a shame that we didn't win." I can't bring myself to name such consumers - stay. They are more like dubious landlords who do not know if they will move into the apartment or even look at it.
